There is one scope ddoc per scope
This ddoc is a template and is not usually installed. Instead it is copied and modified by the control application

for testing purposes, to manually install this design doc in a couchdb database 

    install couchapp

    $ cd meo_my/ddoc/culture

    edit  user, password, host and db in .couchapprc default db string
        "default" : {
          "db" : "http://user:password@127.0.0.1:5984/db"
        },

    $ couchapp push 
